eventSummary:
The FBI issued an urgent warning regarding a 'quishing' (QR code phishing) campaign where a hacking group is targeting U.S. entities with malicious emails containing fraudulent QR codes.
Sources:
- https://www.tomsguide.com/computing/online-security/dont-scan-that-qr-code-fbi-warns-hackers-adding-malicious-qr-links-in-emails
